{"tid":305322,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"大家倒車泊車時有咩祕訣易泊啲？","createTime":"2017-07-01T14:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T02:01:27.000Z","uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcdf3f12f30d06e5405615570164aec6e18902f","tid":305322,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"除左聽聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg&h=7c37195d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"353581d82465d5942873b689a55b395b5e1fe247","tid":305322,"uid":30929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左聽聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg&h=7c37195d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCam"},{"pid":"f24167556a89138ce75d963d2a3afec9bc5e1c95","tid":305322,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"S位定L位？"},{"pid":"3ee86900b2e7bbbb2642d639546bdb2a40fecf66","tid":305322,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>S位定L位？</blockquote><br />\nL 好窄既車場 <br />\n隔離條柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b9f41072f59193bab6769ccea2695846d19f15","tid":305322,"uid":85217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"唔好怕柒 扭多幾手軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54cf01580e1ec7e76fd4fbaf58feb1b33a7fc6c","tid":305322,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb8bfc0f8d066fe99f9becc2e14988fe62ffdc89","tid":305322,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"睇鏡"},{"pid":"eeafee4691da6e94c92039ed171de7a51ce125ee","tid":305322,"uid":30929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"L位 個人泊法<br />\n左邊預最少位 <br />\n左邊預得好 右邊Done <br />\n一手肽都得 <br />\n<br />\n不過按地方而有所改變，我公司同屋企容許唔一定到到都得<br />\n但我當標準去做"},{"pid":"3bd947cfd647dc447e88ee5f129a9ed31baf1ac7","tid":305322,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"睇鏡最準"},{"pid":"7da5c1e3ebb93789ca9c5a75f63daf09ae8b341c","tid":305322,"uid":73123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"唔好怕醜，唔肯定就空波拉手掣落車睇<br />\n撞左柒d定落車睇位柒d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2832373251a8c0439ffa5d8136b9f360ad6b82","tid":305322,"uid":17722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"裝倒泊鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69c557002a7d38b4af0ded9c58a7727e2f7112d","tid":305322,"uid":21462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T23:56:36.000Z","msg":"剩係望一邊鏡"},{"pid":"ab9239677018436b6e609ca409ef3349ba889d23","tid":305322,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:29:39.000Z","msg":"就咁放係馬路"},{"pid":"5310d1a5f8038f29cf83fb93870e4be46413b1d0","tid":305322,"uid":36583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"撞柱撞到車尾中間 你手車都好屎吓 坐車算唔好害人"},{"pid":"b2f50445424f39d5519ad1126c1fea48e8ba6b71","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"學車嗰陣師傅教數線，以自己車前座乘客位側鏡對住你想泊個車位向前數第四條線，然後停車，入後波，扭盡軚倒後入<br />\n<br />\n另一種就係側鏡對準車位第二條線，向前扭出45度，然後倒後入"},{"pid":"f34c6433fc06c6a421ffac62c824736d00459276","tid":305322,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"睇到個牆係你背後1cm 停"},{"pid":"f26e22a6b53bf425519d40e07b89b0ea9fd77bff","tid":305322,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"以前覺得好難，自從有左大螢幕車Cam兼啲虛線指示，基本上易過食豆<br />\n但如果而家叫我揸返冇Cam嘅車，我真係未必有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0fcd830c721c8b79d5cd8df7c764e3118f5fd0","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前覺得好難，自從有左大螢幕車Cam兼啲虛線指示，基本上易過食豆<br />\n但如果而家叫我揸返冇Cam嘅車，我真係未必有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n窮撚表示二手車冇cam，beep beep聲都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84913187d77270c6f225fdca5f20c52f4d592ecc","tid":305322,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"拉一拉手制"},{"pid":"4ecbba24018bc94cc46ffe04d2eedda6df0b8e11","tid":305322,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:26:13.000Z","msg":"我泊就睇一邊鏡 貼啲<br />\n咁自然另一邊就唔會撞"},{"pid":"5cdfbcfdcf065c9b8cbecee4732eb798329909ba","tid":305322,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:28:33.000Z","msg":"其實當你熟左架車就好易<br />\n泊車只要有個唔怕柒心態<br />\n扭多幾手落車睇<br />\n入唔到咪d波修正再後入<br />\n入前望下2邊鏡睇下條線距離同埋睇下直唔直<br />\n怕隊屎忽就睇睇對面架車個影 同埋後燈燈影<br />\n再唔得就落車睇下<br />\n慢慢你就掌握到<br />\n反正有牌 你扭10手都冇人理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba4468189cd6ced1b7fadeeeb6ca4c48f7b7235","tid":305322,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"有時渣公司架貨van 得鏡頭<br />\n得尾門上面塊鏡反射 好難睇<br />\n多數落車望 再上車郁 睇兩次乜都得啦"},{"pid":"156bc754979b500aa11835758a9fa46834c70453","tid":305322,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"S位斬尾有冇心得？"},{"pid":"8c656184020dd82f4eb4461f6a943e7f5c5fb6a3","tid":305322,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"部車有鳥瞰圖"},{"pid":"ae5139e50cf3460c44a036cdf7068fe1948b0ced","tid":305322,"uid":75211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇"},{"pid":"5f1a3068ccdf162f0f17d9957e852350629848be","tid":305322,"uid":75211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇</blockquote><br />\n用泊車cam先岩"},{"pid":"f40a43934be39b4ce4b7111462b0909934030aa1","tid":305322,"uid":219,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"通常聽聲 噗左下就停 <br />\n靠感覺就車身chok左chok停"},{"pid":"b7bb113186d9b9ce5f7d9b647f81b6f5fb5fcb25","tid":305322,"uid":29747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"有時撞到D撚樣真係睇住個cam尾貼頭咁貼住黎泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812385481043b3c99a5027f5e932c0dcdd4e90dc","tid":305322,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好怕醜，唔肯定就空波拉手掣落車睇<br />\n撞左柒d定落車睇位柒d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156e74cac60e5f60eaa95d8c20750072e87fa5c1","tid":305322,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"其實架架車都有泊車sesnor 你聽到就到位就好停 <br />\n望下旁邊車個車頭 大約就知到位未"},{"pid":"7d35b944ff77ea511f1e65f51ccafcd6b9427c99","tid":305322,"uid":113749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實架架車都有泊車sesnor 你聽到就到位就好停 <br />\n望下旁邊車個車頭 大約就知到位未</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係架架車都有架"},{"pid":"295863ed8160894ff6f767420b2174f3f42737c7","tid":305322,"uid":104618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"屌柒689"},{"pid":"45f00a97029045f1a69643134c8ef25794fb4ab4","tid":305322,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"心得分享<br />\n<br />\n得閒夜晚去停車場練泊, 唔好怕柒扭多幾手<br />\n肯定左近柱果邊唔撞之後就睇司機位鏡同地下條線對位<br />\n之後用隔離車司機位benchmark番泊前/後<br />\n<br />\n最緊要練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8662549a0b35fe7406986bfe4d09f11f17e61bd3","tid":305322,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d4bad3214694ea4556c4701a066fd327897e4c1","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>S位斬尾有冇心得？</blockquote><br />\n我都想問<br />\n學van唔識睇私家車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補鐘師傅教睇後車窗位，睇到前車車尾再多少少就開始扭咁......<br />\n有冇人可以指導下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3947bb07760a126976a7ccdf4c9a0a6c3a45ab","tid":305322,"uid":113749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>S位斬尾有冇心得？</blockquote><br />\n我都想問<br />\n學van唔識睇私家車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補鐘師傅教睇後車窗位，睇到前車車尾再多少少就開始扭咁......<br />\n有冇人可以指導下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打斜入會易好多 條路太窄頭入扭返出黎再泊入去"},{"pid":"a70b7084723461422cc64730148cf752cf8eae8d","tid":305322,"uid":7843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇</blockquote><br />\n用泊車cam先岩</blockquote><br />\n師兄咁叻仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下我"},{"pid":"7f9616016d6d28e11d0f6be67afb30a8ebe7f350","tid":305322,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CUaVhBSFO28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCUaVhBSFO28&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=01f09052\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CUaVhBSFO28</a>"},{"pid":"e7e20f6ef07b8d38f76b6f8e59377427564e4611","tid":305322,"uid":58277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"你確定到個車位夠大就偷位打斜架車入L位，剩係睇司機果邊鏡就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離有車嘅話咪對返佢塊鏡位停就多數無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無車，部車入位扭直左就開門伸個頭出去望尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733f0f396c9e81d6d58b2014d77519cd3d2e4bba","tid":305322,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"我部二手車無sensor，個泊位cam唔啱位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己泊車唔叻，但主要靠左右鏡去泊<br />\n<br />\n其實真係最緊要熟自己架車<br />\n一路泊一路構想現場實況<br />\n其實會抽到個mind出黎好似CCTV角度去睇住自己泊車咁 (可能講到1999)"},{"pid":"846f9d0e1bb8b365c900557973cf2dbf48c5828f","tid":305322,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇</blockquote><br />\n用泊車cam先岩</blockquote><br />\n師兄咁叻仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下我</blockquote><br />\n文字上唔識點教你<br />\n但係可以講小小秘訣<br />\n架車幾長幾闊自己一定要清楚<br />\n1.唔理S位/L位 有幾遠距離/空間比你泊就好好善用<br />\n2.好好善用你既左右鏡 因為咩時候睇得最清楚既就係左右鏡(而唔係車cam)<br />\n3.車慢軚快 唔夠比啲唔夠比啲 扭幾多手都無問題 唔好阻人就得<br />\n4.靠車cam 同sensor 真係垃圾到不得了(如果慣左手勢 換第部無sensor同垃圾有咩分別<br />\n5.操泊位架車越大越好"},{"pid":"2e0cf2c2c2e05df1a5d746011485c01e51456f4d","tid":305322,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"L位易泊<br />\nS位泊街先難，特別係窄街<br />\n你第一野扭盡倒車時<br />\n窄車好易high到隔黎泊路邊既車"},{"pid":"36db0090c2cc6bf1680cf7d9fd4e1a02d2f3fe3b","tid":305322,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇</blockquote><br />\n用泊車cam先岩</blockquote><br />\n師兄咁叻仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下我</blockquote><br />\n文字上唔識點教你<br />\n但係可以講小小秘訣<br />\n架車幾長幾闊自己一定要清楚<br />\n1.唔理S位/L位 有幾遠距離/空間比你泊就好好善用<br />\n2.好好善用你既左右鏡 因為咩時候睇得最清楚既就係左右鏡(而唔係車cam)<br />\n3.車慢軚快 唔夠比啲唔夠比啲 扭幾多手都無問題 唔好阻人就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.靠車cam 同sensor 真係垃圾到不得了(如果慣左手勢 換第部無sensor同垃圾有咩分別</span><br />\n5.操泊位架車越大越好</blockquote><br />\n自己揸架唔夠4m車仔，有後波cam<br />\n當揸公司d貨van無cam無sensor最多只可以望尾鏡黎泊街真係興奮到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599bc86eb817eb49903cf564b9d50a37736fac18","tid":305322,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左聽聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F223643_fd557013f0e6f65a47f79596d84465c0.jpg&h=7c37195d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n望側鏡<br />\n去判斷倒入的方位岩唔岩<br />\n路闊 45度入<br />\n路窄 90度<br />\n<br />\n如果你係我附近<br />\n可以教下你睇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3b980a476d265b90a2f9c1564d76d6814cbda1","tid":305322,"uid":3937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"雖然蝗語<br />\n但可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgkf2Mi3w0vo&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=baf94ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo</a>"},{"pid":"5200b156bf69729f25abf74ef95b57a117f197dd","tid":305322,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg&h=8bb280fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea74633b006b7c974a3925eca74833a1bf27834","tid":305322,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg&h=8bb280fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞咩嚟？"},{"pid":"b497724f399a61ff5d3cde76caabb730b4462081","tid":305322,"uid":98503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"哩多好多新牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熟能生巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5612072e855c7129d5866a0e83e4ba4b6ca6cc","tid":305322,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg&h=8bb280fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d31a488e78e1d552c5e41d0133eeaeeffd39c54","tid":305322,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F122216_486ceaf4707ccf3f8e44e007dd09521b.jpg&h=8bb280fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞咩嚟？</blockquote><br />\n係西貢長命斜尾入大油左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf09faa2a0a756f63f629047fd7beb7cfaf8fc4","tid":305322,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用泊車後鏡睇先係最唔識泊車既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸車靠感覺 你要知道架車身幾長<br />\n幾多頭 幾多尾<br />\n睇返左右鏡就泊到架喇</blockquote><br />\n用泊車cam先岩</blockquote><br />\n師兄咁叻仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下我</blockquote><br />\n文字上唔識點教你<br />\n但係可以講小小秘訣<br />\n架車幾長幾闊自己一定要清楚<br />\n1.唔理S位/L位 有幾遠距離/空間比你泊就好好善用<br />\n2.好好善用你既左右鏡 因為咩時候睇得最清楚既就係左右鏡(而唔係車cam)<br />\n3.車慢軚快 唔夠比啲唔夠比啲 扭幾多手都無問題 唔好阻人就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.靠車cam 同sensor 真係垃圾到不得了(如果慣左手勢 換第部無sensor同垃圾有咩分別</span><br />\n5.操泊位架車越大越好</blockquote><br />\n自己揸架唔夠4m車仔，有後波cam<br />\n當揸公司d貨van無cam無sensor最多只可以望尾鏡黎泊街真係興奮到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貨VAN真係好易泊位"},{"pid":"6efe9fb421e7353a2becd8414f91c0d2c2fd3d9c","tid":305322,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打習慣成含頭拎去段面黎泊車?<br />\n即係小望2邊鏡<br />\n主要係成個人向後望"},{"pid":"0e32819a80ea0783d9856437c27992574867f77b","tid":305322,"uid":1715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打習慣成含頭拎去段面黎泊車?<br />\n即係小望2邊鏡<br />\n主要係成個人向後望</blockquote><br />\n望鏡望唔哂就要望後 唔好太依賴個sensor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81d6176f0973405dbfe2c4f06788946ca180ea3","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打習慣成含頭拎去段面黎泊車?<br />\n即係小望2邊鏡<br />\n主要係成個人向後望</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鏡係判斷左右與物件嘅距離，拎後望係判斷車尾嘅距離。所以泊L位應該係先望晒左右後確定安全，倒後轉時主要望左右鏡，回直後主要拎後望。<br />\n利申: 9up"},{"pid":"4a693be0b33c3fc8196dec91c1e170dd1e100c11","tid":305322,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"L位易過S位好多"},{"pid":"211dce86ba0806fb4742f58a1c9e6a640d8648d7","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>L位易過S位好多</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學車學完泊S位都係唔識泊街位<br />\n前車長度、闊度、埋得開/埋、彎位都有影響，千變萬化"},{"pid":"5bf626ea6d9075654ff92130cc9ed1a852216616","tid":305322,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"比錢人地泊"},{"pid":"ed32eb880d60ebb697f80b5173b5faeb7cacd562","tid":305322,"uid":43239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:36:24.000Z","msg":"L位都泊成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3ac396bd109db5fe6830bef6e71279ee62f773","tid":305322,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"S位我都係跟網上教學喳<br />\n<br />\n利申:fit仔"},{"pid":"84546e6e9d4fc16a24081c4aa49d310c677deafb","tid":305322,"uid":20602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"L位唔怕柒, 扭兩手實入到。唔好貪心一手扭入去一般都唔難。尤其L位九成係停車場位。<br />\n<br />\nS位真係憑感覺。上網睇過教學片都冇咩用。尤其係你在街等到位,S扭入去之際, 後車不斷呠你, 果下真係好考心理質素 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4c8f04ca423a26fe65cf449694b0145c157a34","tid":305322,"uid":39805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前覺得好難，自從有左大螢幕車Cam兼啲虛線指示，基本上易過食豆<br />\n但如果而家叫我揸返冇Cam嘅車，我真係未必有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我從來都唔睇後泊 cam 去泊車, 佢既作用只係俾我去睇下後方有無矮少障礙物同有無人行過<br />\n<br />\n泊我自己車位我就索性熄埋 parking sensor, 因為非常貼牆只識長 beep<br />\n<br />\n永遠睇鏡係最實際"},{"pid":"f49f937b7ef7242854732678a49ce17361e6bd3d","tid":305322,"uid":109263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T21:49:29.000Z","msg":"倒車時睇實一邊鏡，慢慢入<br />\n間中停車睇另一邊鏡，睇清楚冇人冇物再倒車<br />\n唔好亂扭呔，新手好易搞錯啲方向<br />\n唔好怕樣衰，冇信心既話寧願扭多幾手呔，甚至落車睇位都唔好夾硬嚟"},{"pid":"9304a8193554ebf81bbe01419f399dc77429ac17","tid":305322,"uid":99585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T22:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然蝗語<br />\n但可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgkf2Mi3w0vo&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=baf94ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo</a></blockquote><br />\n之前考車師傅教漏咗一個parking, 又咁啱考車嘅時候考官就係考無教到果個parking , 好彩之前我有上youtube 睇到呢條片, 跟住pass咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68828b9f5fec206937b195cb45091bca3351a3d","tid":305322,"uid":87182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c87111ce896ea4603c167ceb58839fb0de383ae","tid":305322,"uid":401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"買部乜撚都無既爛車返來練，hi多幾次就熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b6088e6aec3de0c81735edd09cb43c68ea4756","tid":305322,"uid":109799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:28:53.000Z","msg":"開窗大叫 [睇撚住啊！]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f96f7233ea6492f23523f4ae4c349ec90a6d17c","tid":305322,"uid":27852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:40:01.000Z","msg":"睇住後轆位置就會易泊好多"},{"pid":"70ef100692f98bcc91d4c4b3c46fa418be4d6c49","tid":305322,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開窗大叫 [睇撚住啊！]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同條柱講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0677fa4e48972ac1641d9e892ed6db6cb9e24f5d","tid":305322,"uid":9766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"當年錢七寶馬後泊時候左邊鏡會較落到去睇地下同後車方便好多，而且無後泊，感應一時有聲一時無 就係咁既問題先至訓練到睇位泊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dd9b34a840b0b600c881d4780ab0149738df93","tid":305322,"uid":11868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"渣慣左，知架車約莫幾大之後，而家泊咩位都係求撚其，唔得扭多兩手算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a4714eb0dfa7b3bcca6ce8ac1c35a44fd15cbc","tid":305322,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"個人心得<br />\nL 位有位偷就唔好L字入, 無位偷就練多幾手<br />\nS位免得過都唔泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c5285445315a3f9e5f68fda9a1f914d33ce4ba","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然蝗語<br />\n但可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgkf2Mi3w0vo&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=baf94ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gkf2Mi3w0vo</a></blockquote><br />\n之前考車師傅教漏咗一個parking, 又咁啱考車嘅時候考官就係考無教到果個parking , 好彩之前我有上youtube 睇到呢條片, 跟住pass咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nS位太貼壆喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且應該點判斷45度角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97ab1091e45c980dcb5d4d593ec5fbddfd88ef9","tid":305322,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"同問點定45度角"},{"pid":"4cd7073da9c46a09260a96af54206f492323d789","tid":305322,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問點定45度角</blockquote><br />\n有種教法係，你扭軚之前搵定一個位於45度位置嘅目標，例如燈柱。當你倒後轉入去車位時，該目標去到擋風玻璃中間時，就回直軚繼續入<br />\n<br />\n但之後入多幾多先要再扭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047bc43937c60ed9b84064b6754a325ba25b616a","tid":305322,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ptbk1iqg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fptbk1iqg&h=49de9699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}